@c ===beg===
@c u: expand ((x + y)^6);
@c diff (%, x);
@c integrate (1/(1 + x^3), x);
@c ===end===
@example
@group
(%i1) u: expand ((x + y)^6);
       6        5       2  4       3  3       4  2      5      6
